119
00:06:22.799 --> 00:06:23.966
From time to time?

120
00:06:23.967 --> 00:06:26.177
Hey. you know what?

121
00:06:26.178 --> 00:06:28.095
I'm just glad that at least one person

122
00:06:28.096 --> 00:06:30.473
