still remembers Tia's birthdays.

123
00:06:30.474 --> 00:06:33.017
- Oh.
- Oh. my God. It was one time.

124
00:06:33.018 --> 00:06:34.894
She's only had one birthday
since she died.

125
00:06:34.895 --> 00:06:38.189
