for missed dead mom birthdays.

126
00:06:38.190 --> 00:06:39.774
Your mom loved her birthdays so much.

127
00:06:39.775 --> 00:06:42.068
Mmm. Now you're making me sad.

128
00:06:42.069 --> 00:06:44.696
