181
00:09:33.198 --> 00:09:35.700
So. it's-it's more like a "vomelet".

182
00:09:35.701 --> 00:09:38.995
Oh. use that with your friends
and tell me if it goes viral.

183
00:09:38.996 --> 00:09:40.913
- Be older.
- Bitch.

184
00:09:40.914 --> 00:09:44.083
Brian wanted to come with. and I thought
